TITLE: F3 Innovate
DESCRIPTION: F3 Innovate supports industry R&D with the nation’s premiere research institutions in the place where specialty crops and tech thrive. Students are trained in research and graduate ready to join the future of food workforce.

TITLE: 2023 EDGE in tech symposium
DESCRIPTION: The 7th Annual Edge in Tech Symposium was held virtually on March 2nd, 2023. This year’s overarching theme was Smarter Tech for a Resilient Future.
